<HEADLINE>
WOMEN WIN BIG AT GRAMMY AWARDS
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
BY GLENN WHIPP  
 c.1999 Los Angeles Daily News  
<TEXT>
<P>
