<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-02-25 14:02 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9090 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-WHITE-COLUMN-BOS &LR;      02-25 0666
