the long bond was down 1 5/32 point, with the yield at 5.59
percent. The industrial average was down 65 points, or 0.7 percent,
and the Nasdaq index was down 17 points, or 0.7 percent. Elsewhere,
prices rose 0.8 percent in Tokyo and fell 0.2 percent in Hong Kong.
