   &QR;  Chattanooga _ The Hunter Museum of American Art presents
``Seeing Jazz,'' a traveling exhibition organized by the
Smithsonian Institution. Includes a variety of artistic responses
to jazz through paintings, sculpture, photographs, collage,
drawings and literature. Through April 4. 423-267-0968.
