   CONGRESS-FOREIGN-POLICY (Washington) _ State Department and
Pentagon officials testify before Senate and House committees:
House International Relations Committee hears Secretary Albright;
Senate Arms Services hears Pickering, the under secretary of state.
By Eric Schmitt.
