   ISRAEL-POLITICS (Jerusalem) _ The Wye accord with the
Palestinians becomes a political football in the Israeli campaign:
Prime Minister Netanayahu offered to carry out some of the accord,
but Palestinians reject the moves as minor. By Deborah Sontag.
