<P>
   CUBA-LETTER _ WASHINGTON _ Florida Sens. Connie Mack and Bob
Graham sent a letter Thursday to Secretary of State Madeleine
Albright urging her to introduce a resolution condemning Cuba for
human rights violations when the United Nations Commission on Human
Rights meets in Geneva. (Lipman, Cox News Service)
