   IMMIGRATION _ WASHINGTON _ Two weeks after Rep. Lamar Smith,
R-Texas, threatened to seek the resignation of Immigration and
Naturalization Service Commissioner Doris Meissner, the chairman of
the House immigration and claims subcommittee pledged Thursday to
seek more money for her budget. (Mollison, Cox News Service). 20
</P>
