<P>
   LEGAL-DEFENSE-FUND _ AUSTIN _ Texas contributors to the Bill
Clinton legal defense fund range from the famous to the obscure.
They include former U.S. House Speaker Jim Wright, who gave $100,
to hundreds of retired teachers and current college professors, to
one Grand Prairie man who gave $1.69. We talk to some folks about
why they gave and what they think now. (Herman, Austin
American-Statesman).
