   These pages, in three popular formats (DTI, PDF, Quark), come
from CoxNet, the news service of Cox Newspapers, a partner of The
New York Times News Service. The layouts are readily adaptable to
your own design and ad space.
</P>
<P>
   During the NASCAR season, NASCAR pages can be downloaded
Thursday afternoon for Sunday's race.
</P>
