http://nytsyn.com/pageexpress and click on ``preview and download
pages.'' To download a sample page, get the password by contacting
Sales Director Bob Farnell by phone, 212-499-3335, or e-mail,
farnellb(AT)nytimes.com.
</P>
<P>
   Thank you.
</P>
<P>
   _ The New York Times Syndicate.
</P>
