<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-LADN-SPORTS-BUDGET- </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>


</HEADLINE>
  The Los Angeles Daily News plans to move the following sports
stories for use by NYTimes News Service clients, AMs and PMs of
Feb. 26 and thereafter. For questions about stories, resends or
inquiries, call Brad Nelson at (818) 713-3602. 
 
 
BKN-LAKERS (Anaheim, Calif.) _ The new-look Lakers with Bill Bertka
at the helm and Dennis Rodman on the bench are at the Clippers in
Anaheim. 7:30 p.m.
<TEXT>
<P>
   By Howard Beck. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.)
</P>
<P>
   BKN-LAKENOTES (Anaheim, Calif.) _ Notes on the Lakers. w/advance
capsule
</P>
<P>
